{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986680/extras/s1_600.png?t=1677071247\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986680/extras/story_gif.gif?t=1677071247\" /><br>In Taiwan, early 1954, an orphan was taken in by a temple. Upon overhearing of his past, he set out in the darkness of night on a &quot;fantastic journey&quot; to find his relatives. Those at the temple were none the wiser. He grew from hiding from ghosts to fighting ghouls. During his journey, he uncovered a ghost town's past and shocking truths.<br><br>Events are based on real people and history. The tale contains the blood, sweat, and tears of this land, along with a worldview in which the ghostly plane can be interacted with.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986680/extras/s2_600.png?t=1677071247\" /><br>Immerse yourself in a rich 3D action-adventure game with 3D third-person gameplay. Players will arm themselves as they traverse the thrilling atmosphere of a ghost town.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986680/extras/s3_600.png?t=1677071247\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986680/extras/Sequence_skill_gif.gif?t=1677071247\" /><br>\u2022 Gameplay demonstrating martial arts straight from modern practitioners and masters. State-of-the-art motion capture technology allows players to experience the true power of Taiwanese martial arts.<br>\u2022 Spells are based on Taoist practices, reproduced digitally under the guidance of Taoist priests.<br>\u2022 Solve unique puzzles and beat mini-games that combine elements of Taiwanese culture and religion, such as moon blocks and the Tao's divine bagua.<br>\u2022 Take in a new musical style that merges oriental musical instruments with metal and electronic music. The soundtrack has been professionally produced to induce a movie-like enjoyment.<br>\u2022 The haunted houses and temples within are real. The production team personally scouted these areas and conducted field investigations, experiencing many &quot;spiritual phenomena&quot; along the way.<br>\u2022 Support for multiple languages, including Traditional Chinese, English, Japanese, Korean, Russian, French, German, Spanish and Portuguese.<br>\u2022 Supports Windows","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Buddha Smiles upon You","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/986680/7557caf4fdda441e69658c1e70635643c1dc6616.jpg"},{"name":"Divine Permission!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/986680/e848800196b428a52e593d7b49d757abd19c5dc6.jpg"},{"name":"Justice Shall Prevail","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/986680/74f44f4b89af1a7e97f9d6dbf819c1a9cbf1135c.jpg"},{"name":"Die Hard, Live Harder","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/986680/0a3a2991376c319d0fe91d015deeba73f165b40b.jpg"},{"name":"Entry-Level Taoist Priest","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/986680/ef47af705fc9dbf3eebc2831dc0a26ff3e7a11e5.jpg"},{"name":"Lam Ching-Ying","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/986680/5b5824c59547ea203970b58b47c7dd188d90fdbe.jpg"},{"name":"Jhong Kuei","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/986680/aab6c959ffd2be97df9d1fe61b599ad7b9fa739c.jpg"},{"name":"Goddess of Radio","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/986680/cdf844b1c2fbc3fe465acbd548dd561f4221e8d7.jpg"},{"name":"Items to the Rescue!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/986680/df0e2820d603c51d74de319ac091753ee1c0cc9a.jpg"},{"name":"Death, 